   As the LUMI/25.09 stack uses a version of the programming environment
   that is newer than the current default on the system (25.03), please be
   aware of https://lumi-supercomputer.github.io/LUMI-training-materials/2day-20251020/102-CPE/#warning-1-you-do-not-always-get-what-you-expect
